snippet.title: Early Access Trailer | Star Chef Simulator
snippet.description:
Have you ever dreamed of running your own restaurant? Then your dream is about to come true! Set up and manage your restaurant with staff, equipment and more in Star Chef Simulator - Coming to Steam on August 30th.

2024 Star Chef Simulator published by Pinguin Games and developed by Division Software
Music created with Udio
